replies.body:
It's funny that the second AD assassins get countered by shields, the forums go apeshit. But AP assassins have had to deal with {{item:3155}} {{item:3156}} for over a year now with all the ADs defending it to their dying breath.

At least {{item:3190}} {{item:3401}} {{champion:40}} and CoC require actual keystrokes and timing instead of passively proccing the second it looks like the AD might possibly lose a fight.

Because what the game totally needs is more lethality items than {{item:3147}} {{item:3814}} {{item:3036}} {{item:3033}} {{item:3071}} {{item:3142}} 

Because the game is totally flush with mpen items that an assassin would ever build {{item:3020}} {{item:3135}} 

But yes....more niche lethality items, please, because ADs don't have anything to choose from to deal with a shield. Give me a break.
